isis.stitle: TSI 03-12-19 - Performance Specifications for 2003 Model Year International® Engines

subjectgroup.subject: Performance Specifications for 2003 Model Year International® Engines

geninfo.para: The following performance specifications apply to all 2003 model year International® DT 466, DT 530 and HT 530 engines starting with serial number 1389992.
This TSI should be placed in the proper section of the EGES 215 Diagnostic Manual in Appendix (A), Performances Specifications.
This TSI will update and identify 2003 model year engine family emission documents.

entry.para: International® DT 466, DT 530 and HT 530 (all ratings)
Measure water temperature differential across the radiator with engine on a chassis dynamometer, at full load and ambient temperature of 27°C (80°F) or above.
Full open temperature, 8 mm (0.315 in) stroke

para.emph: Note: If grade No. 1-D is not available, use a winterized or climatized Grade No. 2-D fuel. This is made by blending Grade No. 1-D with No. 2-D fuel to match the temperature conditions in your area.
